TATE
v.
N.C. DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY. No. 437P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Jan. 28, 2016. Herman V. Tate, Hoffman, for Tate, Herman V. Marc X. Sneed, Assistant Attorney General, for N.C. Department Of Public Safety.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 30th of December 2015 by Plaintiff to Safeguard Constitutional Rights:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 28th of January 2016."
